review: Reasonable people will like this place just fine. The complaints I've seen on here so far are ridiculous. State law says you can't smoke on the balconies, and I support that law 1000%. Postmarks on mail returning your deposit money often

author: Ivan Zhuk
review: Horrible apartment management. Waay too expensive for the price. Club house needs to be fixed & yet they charge you extra to use it. Very poor noise quality absorption. Every neighbor can be heard that surrounds you. They say their willing to work with you but do not give you any benefit of the doubt even during a crisis situation!

author: Carson Gregory
review: I do not recommend living here. You will be harassed constantly. If you are a smoker, you can't use the balcony you PAY FOR! Nosey neighbors! RUDE management! We have  been moved out for 5 days and our phones wont stop ringing. (apartment in perfect condition, so no reason to contact us continuously) Do not rent from these people.

author: Christopher De Rosa
review: My wife and I lived in this apartment complex for 6+ years. We brought home 2 babies to this home. When we first moved in, the original owners and management were fantastic. We never had a single issue.

author: Christie Mickelson
review: Too expensive for how cheaply built it is. You can literally hear your neighbors sneeze and I could hear  my upstairs neighbor every single time he took a step, I could hear his blender in the morning. Also, they entered my apartment seven times in five months, always for some stupid reason. Anything is better than this.
